<note n="0907004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0907004">能＝而【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0907005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0907005">〔忽〕－【宮】</note>
